4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience, aiming to develop them into cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes weekly with a maximum of 16 students per class. Students will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical training in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Successful graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Instruction is available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop